1
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:12,160
Say it.

2
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:13,680
What do you want?

3
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:16,200
Speak up.

4
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:16,840
Let go first.

5
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:18,360
Let go first.

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:21,080
Come on.

7
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:27,640
What a fool.

8
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,200
What do you want to know?

9
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:34,760
You're a rich young man.

10
00:00:34,760 --> 00:00:35,800
You come here

11
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:38,960
just for this?

12
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,320
You're choking me just for this?

13
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,200
I'm speechless.

14
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,160
This is a contract.

15
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:47,640
Contract. Do you understand?

16
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:50,800
Contract?

17
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,520
That's right.

18
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:56,480
This is a contract between me and my idol.

19
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,960
Sun God.

20
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,440
Young Master?

21
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,080
That's right.

22
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:17,880
It's me.

23
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,480
I finally saw you, my idol.

24
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,320
I should be the first person in the world

25
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:27,160
to see you in person.

26
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:28,080
Without further ado,

27
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,320
let's have a game.

28
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,200
One on one.

29
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,720
I never play games myself.

30
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,240
You don't play games yourself?

31
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,320
You find a substitute player?

32
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:38,200
What substitute player can be so good?

33
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:39,360
I collected

34
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,120
all the data of the game masters,

35
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,080
and designed a

36
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:44,240
highest comprehensive level of idling program.

37
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,320
Including all the game memories

38
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,040
on your computer now,

39
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,320
I can analyze them all.

40
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,200
High-tech.

41
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,480
Every step can be

42
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,360
precisely predicted by my operation.

43
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,520
This is too awesome.

44
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:11,039
It's worth being your number one for so many years.

45
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,160
Idol.

46
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,480
Please take me as your disciple.

47
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,680
Do you want to learn?

48
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,760
Of course.

49
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,600
I will repay the tuition

50
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,000
tenfold.

51
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,480
That's a lot of money.

52
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,080
Something happened.

53
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,320
I want to play the ultimate game.

54
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,040
Sounds exciting.

55
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,680
No problem with the tuition.

56
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,560
I must come along.

57
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,160
I'll do it even if it's dangerous.

58
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,280
So dangerous?

59
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,120
Very dangerous.

60
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,680
Then it's even more exciting.

61
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,840
I must do it.

62
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,400
Can I know why?

63
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,640
Because they killed my brother.

64
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,440
I see.

65
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,080
It's a blood feud.

66
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,200
I must revenge.

67
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,680
I'll kill them.

68
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,520
I didn't expect you to be so just.

69
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,520
Of course.

70
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,080
Am I

71
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,600
so easy to be seen through by you?

72
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,080
What kind of person are you?

73
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,080
You're a muscle head

74
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,920
with a simple mind.

75
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,600
You always want to use violence.

76
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,640
You just pinched my neck.

77
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,400
Is that right?

78
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,880
Shouldn't you apologize to me?

79
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,160
A gentleman uses his mouth, not his hands.

80
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,080
Don't you know?

81
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,560
You're back.

82
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,480
He Xiaochen knows our plan.

83
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,920
Look at his expression.

84
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,040
He looks so confident.

85
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,360
He must have dealt with it.

86
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,000
Young Master Zhang,

87
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,840
sell all the paintings

88
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,880
you have now.

89
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,760
Jia Yu,

90
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,360
follow the plan

91
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,440
to infiltrate Cixin Orphanage

92
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,160
and collect information.

93
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,000
The more detailed, the better.

94
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,560
And Ye Zhiqiu,

95
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,360
we may have to

96
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,480
deal with Zhen Shida directly,

97
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,040
We can't let him

98
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,440
stay with Zhen Shida.

99
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,120
Don't worry.

100
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,360
I've already arranged it.

101
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,840
Useless.

102
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,480
The joint exhibition ended so abruptly.

103
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,680
How are you managing this?

104
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:00,840
Mr. Zhen,

105
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,240
it was really an emergency.

106
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,600
I was worried about your collection

107
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,240
getting damaged,

108
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,080
so I stopped the exhibition in time.

109
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,880
But,

110
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,320
but I've already talked to James.

111
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,720
We'll find a suitable time

112
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,360
to reopen the exhibition.

113
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:12,920
I don't think that's necessary.

114
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,480
Right?

115
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,640
You just wanted your work

116
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,640
to be featured in this exhibition, right?

117
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,519
Let me tell you, Ye Zhiqiu.

118
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,640
Listen carefully.

119
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,160
You're not cut out for this.

120
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,840
Did you hear that?

121
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:37,800
Mr. Ye,

122
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,520
I've been reflecting on your work.

123
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,600
I have an idea.

124
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,320
I'd like to invite you to join our Zhang's Gallery

125
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,960
abroad creation center,

126
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,880
and sign a contract

127
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,680
as a full-time painter under our gallery.

128
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:48,960
You...

129
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:51,960
Are you serious?

130
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,240
I've already prepared the contract.

131
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,560
As long as you're willing,

132
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,000
we can sign it tomorrow.

133
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,760
Okay.

134
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,880
I'm in.

135
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,280
I'll go tomorrow.

136
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,640
The manager of Zhang's Antique Gallery

137
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,280
has already booked his flight.

138
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:17,080
And Zhen Shida will never find him.

139
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,520
But, everyone,

140
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:20,600
who should we worry about the most now?

141
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,560
Do you know?

142
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,520
Me.

143
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,600
Zhang Xiaoshao.

144
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,120
What's wrong with you?

145
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,160
It takes time to sell paintings.

146
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,920
I have to open my mom's vault first,

147
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,400
then the start-up funds for the second step can be in place.

148
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,000
Without bait,

149
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,520
the fish won't bite.

150
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:42,960
Unless...

151
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,040
People

152
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:49,800
become great because of their dreams.

153
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,680
And my dream

154
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:54,160
is to become a

155
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:56,440
trainee.

156
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,200
This is the only dream

157
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,360
supports.

158
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,440
So as long as she sees

159
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,800
that I'm working hard for my passion,

160
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,280
sacrificing everything for it,

161
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,680
I'll have a chance to get the money.

162
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,760
Mom, this...

163
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,480
Shao.

164
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,200
Just the three of you?

165
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:18,360
These are my teammates.

166
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,560
Xiaoyu.

167
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:20,400
Hello, ma'am.

168
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,280
I'm Xiaoyu.

169
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,600
Hello, auntie.

170
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,280
I'm the stage director for them.

171
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,240
My surname is Wang.

172
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,680
So handsome!

173
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,400
I thought

174
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,760
you were also his teammate.

175
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,840
I heard from Shaoye

176
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,800
that you're very concerned about his progress.

177
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,360
So I specially invited you today

178
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,120
to see their results.

179
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,160
Your son

180
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,360
is really very talented

181
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,200
and very hardworking.

182
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,680
Then show me a dance.

183
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,600
Don't try to fool me.

184
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:43,240
Yes.

185
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,040
Alright.

186
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,480
It's really good.

187
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,960
It's starting to look good.

188
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:20,960
Shaoshao,

189
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,360
it seems you really practiced.

190
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,720
It's more than just practicing.

191
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,280
I've been completely transformed.

192
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:27,040
We will invest the best resources

193
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,440
to build this new group.

194
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,480
Their future is limitless.

195
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,640
Did you hear that, mom?

196
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:32,120
I'm about to debut.

197
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,040
Look at all the expenses

198
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,880
for makeup, hair, costumes,

199
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,520
promotions, and training.

200
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,280
It's a lot.

201
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,920
Do you think my current allowance

202
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,080
is enough?

203
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:41,840
Can you raise it?

204
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,280
Okay.

205
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,440
I'll give you a raise.

206
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,880
Then, thanks for taking care of Shao.

207
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,760
Don't worry.

208
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,240
Bye.

209
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,280
Take care, ma'am.

210
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,680
Finally, it's settled.

211
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,120
Strike while the iron's hot.

212
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,680
How about it, Yu?

213
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,160
Teach our Director Wang a dance.

214
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,600
No need.

215
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,480
Check this out.

216
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,240
It's the hottest thing right now.

217
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,360
by Mang Music Future.

218
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,800
It's awesome.

219
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,360
Look.

220
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,760
Past or future?

221
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:17,000
Don't you know Mang Music Future?

222
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,760
I don't feel it.

223
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,640
I don't care about this.

224
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,000
Fine.

225
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,200
Let's not dance.

226
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,440
Fine.

227
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,480
Let's go celebrate.

228
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:26,760
Let's go.

229
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,880
Something happened.

230
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:39,919
Young Master Zhang is missing.
